= ChangeLog

== ver 0.3 (2003/12/13)

  * Now Ruby/CERNLIB can be built with Ruby 1.8. (Thanks to Juan Alcaraz.)
  * Use packlib_noshift if it exists.
    Ruby/CERNLIB seems not to work with "shift" libraries after year 2001.
    (Thanks to Juan Alcaraz.)
  * New modules: PHTools, GEANT.
  * Fortran:
    * Fix a bug in CERN::Fortran.close.
  * HBook:
    * Add methods: hproj1, hproj2.
    * New example: subdir.rb.
  * HPlot:
    * Add methods: hplsiz, hplnt, hplnxt, hplusr, hplego, hplpto.
    * Fix a bug in hpltab.
    * Fix a bug in example/dice.rb.
    * New example: hplotlego.rb.
  * Mathlib:
    * Add method: rannor.
  * HBook2:
    * Now subclasses can be made for each class.


== ver 0.2 (2002/5/5)

  * Now complex number is an instance of Complex class.
  * New module: HBook2.
  * Mathlib:
    * Add routines for random number generation.


== ver 0.1 (2002/4/15)

  * Initial release.
  * Included modules:
    * Fortran
    * HBook
    * HIGZ
    * HPlot
    * Mathlib
